About the game:

Insaniquarium Deluxe is a creative underwater adventure with amazing graphics and animated aquarium pets! You'll need to fill the tank and feed the fish to keep them happy, healthy, and growing. Earn money to buy new fish by clicking on falling coins. You'll probably get addicted to the quick-click pace, but be careful not to get gobbled up by the bigger fish. Fight aliens and upgrade weapons, and unlock secret pets as you explore 20 captivating new levels and 4 unique tanks of action-puzzle adventure! Insaniquarium Deluxe is a riot for all ages.
